        <updateDate>2010-10-27T20:04:54Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Personal Exemption Fairness Act of 2010 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to require annual metropolitan statistical area cost-of-living adjustments, beginning after 2010, to the personal tax exemption amount. Directs the Secretary of Labor to determine and publish a cost-of-living index for each metropolitan statistical area. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
